      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Proper deployment of Microsoft Copilot boosts productivity across applications:",
        "Create executive summaries quickly, automate document generation, and receive intelligent text suggestions.",
        "Automate data analysis, explain formulas, format data, identify trends, and reconcile financial data in minutes.",
        "Get meeting summaries in real-time with intelligent suggestions and answers to specific questions during or after calls.",
        "Prioritize emails and Teams messages, summarize crucial conversations, and automate reminders and follow-up actions.",
        "Intelligently design and automate slide formatting with advanced data visualization tools to generate professionally sound presentations.",
        "Automate customer services, sales processes, and boost customer engagement and experience.",
        "Automate workflows, reduce development time, and enhance apps with AI-assisted coding.",
        "Detect vulnerabilities and instantly respond to threats with strengthened overall security measures."
      ],
